etsysDnsResolverMIB.name: etsysDnsResolverMIB

revisions.description: Added a range of 1..100 seconds for etsysDnsResolverQueryTimeout.
The initial version of this MIB module.

etsysDnsResolverMIB.contactinfo: Postal: Enterasys Networks 50 Minuteman Rd. Andover, MA 01810-1008 USA Phone: +1 978 684 1000 E-mail: support@enterasys.com WWW: http://www.enterasys.com
etsysDnsResolverMIB.description: This MIB module defines a portion of the SNMP MIB under the Enterasys Networks enterprise OID pertaining to configuration of the DNS resolution mechanisms on a device.

etsysDnsResolverServiceType.name: etsysDnsResolverServiceType
etsysDnsResolverServiceType.reference: RFC 1123, 'Requirements for Internet Hosts -- Application and Support', Section 6.1.3.1
etsysDnsResolverServiceType.description: The type of DNS resolution service provided: recursiveOnly(1) indicates a stub resolver. iterativeOnly(2) indicates a normal full service resolver. recursiveAndIterative(3) indicates a full-service resolver which performs a mix of recursive and iterative queries.

etsysDnsResolverDomainName.name: etsysDnsResolverDomainName
etsysDnsResolverDomainName.description: The DNS domain name where the device is located. If this object is not set, then all address lookups must provide fully qualified domains.

etsysDnsResolverPrimaryServerAddrType.name: etsysDnsResolverPrimaryServerAddrType
etsysDnsResolverPrimaryServerAddrType.description: The type of data returned by etsysDnsResolverPrimaryServerAddr.

etsysDnsResolverPrimaryServerAddr.name: etsysDnsResolverPrimaryServerAddr
etsysDnsResolverPrimaryServerAddr.description: The network address of the primary name server.

etsysDnsResolverSecondaryServerAddrType.name: etsysDnsResolverSecondaryServerAddrType
etsysDnsResolverSecondaryServerAddrType.description: The type of data returned by etsysDnsResolverSecondaryServerAddr.

etsysDnsResolverSecondaryServerAddr.name: etsysDnsResolverSecondaryServerAddr
etsysDnsResolverSecondaryServerAddr.description: The network address of the secondary name server.

etsysDnsResolverTertiaryServerAddrType.name: etsysDnsResolverTertiaryServerAddrType
etsysDnsResolverTertiaryServerAddrType.description: The type of data returned by etsysDnsResolverTertiaryServerAddr.

etsysDnsResolverTertiaryServerAddr.name: etsysDnsResolverTertiaryServerAddr
etsysDnsResolverTertiaryServerAddr.description: The network address of the tertiary name server.

etsysDnsResolverQuaternaryServerAddrType.name: etsysDnsResolverQuaternaryServerAddrType
etsysDnsResolverQuaternaryServerAddrType.description: The type of data returned by etsysDnsResolverQuaternaryServerAddr.

etsysDnsResolverQuaternaryServerAddr.name: etsysDnsResolverQuaternaryServerAddr
etsysDnsResolverQuaternaryServerAddr.description: The network address of the quaternary name server.

etsysDnsResolverIpv4DnsZone.name: etsysDnsResolverIpv4DnsZone
etsysDnsResolverIpv4DnsZone.description: The DNS zone to use for address to name lookups of IPv4 addresses.

etsysDnsResolverIpv6DnsZone.name: etsysDnsResolverIpv6DnsZone
etsysDnsResolverIpv6DnsZone.description: The DNS zone to use for address to name lookups of IPv6 addresses.

etsysDnsResolverServerPortNumber.name: etsysDnsResolverServerPortNumber
etsysDnsResolverServerPortNumber.description: The port number (0-65535) the resolver uses for DNS queries.

etsysDnsResolverQueryTimeout.name: etsysDnsResolverQueryTimeout
etsysDnsResolverQueryTimeout.description: The number of seconds before a DNS request is retried if the DNS server fails to respond.

etsysDnsResolverQueryRetries.name: etsysDnsResolverQueryRetries
etsysDnsResolverQueryRetries.description: The number of times to retry a lookup request to a DNS server that has not successfully responded. This retry count is per name server, so each configured name server will make etsysDnsResolverQueryRetries attempts before giving up and moving to the next configured server.

etsysDnsResolverEnableStatus.name: etsysDnsResolverEnableStatus
etsysDnsResolverEnableStatus.description: The status of the DNS resolver on this device.

etsysDnsResolverPrimaryGroup.name: etsysDnsResolverPrimaryGroup
etsysDnsResolverPrimaryGroup.description: The group for all devices supporting DNS resolution.

etsysDnsResolverSecondaryGroup.name: etsysDnsResolverSecondaryGroup
etsysDnsResolverSecondaryGroup.description: The group for all devices that support two or more servers for DNS resolution.

etsysDnsResolverTertiaryGroup.name: etsysDnsResolverTertiaryGroup
etsysDnsResolverTertiaryGroup.description: The group for all devices that support three or more servers for DNS resolution.

etsysDnsResolverQuaternaryGroup.name: etsysDnsResolverQuaternaryGroup
etsysDnsResolverQuaternaryGroup.description: The group for all devices that support four servers for DNS resolution.

etsysDnsResolverCompliance.name: etsysDnsResolverCompliance
etsysDnsResolverCompliance.description: The compliance statement for devices that support DNS resolution.
